quran[118]{c,v,t}:
  23,1,“۞ Ndithu apambana okhulupirira (mwa Allah)
  23,2,“Amene amakhudzumuka pa mapemphero awo (poipereka mitima yawo kwa Allah modzichepetsa)
  23,3,“Ndi omwe amapewa zinthu zopanda pake (zachabe)
  23,4,“Ndi omwe amakwaniritsa (nsanamira ya) chopereka (Zakaat)
  23,5,“Ndi omwe amasunga umaliseche wawo
  23,6,“Kupatula kwa akazi awo ndi adzakazi omwe manja awo akumanja apeza. Choncho iwo (pakukumana ndi amenewo) saali odzudzulidwa
  23,7,“Koma omwe angafune zosemphana ndi izi (kulumikizana ndi mkazi posiya njira ziwirizi) iwowo ndiwo opyola malire (a Allah)
  23,8,“Ndi amene amasunga malonjezo awo ndi zomwe akhulupirika nazo
  23,9,“Ndi omwe akusunga mapemphero awo (popemphera mu nthawi zake ndi kutsata malamulo ake uku ali odzichepetsa)
  23,10,“Iwo ndi olandira (zabwino tsiku la Qiyâma)
  23,11,“Amene adzalandira Munda wamtendere (wotchedwa) Fir’dausi (Munda wapamwamba kwambiri). M’menemo iwo adzakhala nthawi yaitali
  23,12,“Ndipo ndithu tidamlenga munthu kuchokera ku dongo labwino
  23,13,“Kenako tidalenga ana ake ndi dontho lamadzi (ambewu ya munthu) lomwe lidaikidwa pamalo osungidwa
  23,14,"“Kenako tidalisintha dontholo kukhala magazi oundana; ndipo kenako magaziwo tidawasintha kukhala m’nofu; ndipo kenako m’nofu tidausintha kukhala mafupa; ndipo mafupawo tidawaveka minofu, kenako tidamsintha kukhala cholengedwa china. Choncho watukuka Allah, Wabwino polenga"
  23,15,“Kenako ndithu inu pambuyo pa zimenezo mudzamwalira
  23,16,"“Ndithu inu, kenako mudzaukitsidwa pa tsiku la Qiyâma"
  23,17,"“Ndipo ndithu tapanga njira zisanu ndi ziwiri (mitambo) pamwamba panu, ndipo ndithu (Ife) sitisiya kulabadira zolengedwa"
  23,18,"“Ndipo tatsitsa madzi mwamuyeso kuchokera kumwamba, ndi kuwakhazikitsa m’nthaka; ndipo ndithu Ife ndi okhoza kuwachotsa (kuti musathandizike nawo, koma sitidachite zimenezo chifukwa chokuchitirani chifundo)"
  23,19,"“Ndi madzi amenewo, tidakupangirani minda ya kanjedza ndi mpesa, m’menemo inu mulinazo zipatso zambiri; ndipo mwazimenezo mumadya"
  23,20,"“Ndipo (tidakupangirani) mtengo womera pa phiri la Sinai, womwe umatulutsa mafuta; ndipo ndindiwo kwa amene amadya. (Mtengo wake ndi mzitona)"
  23,21,“Ndipo ndithu m’ziweto muli lingaliro kwa inu. Timakumwetsani zomwe zili m’mimba mwake; ndipo m’zimenezo mukupeza zothandiza zambiri; ndipo zina mwa izo mumadya
  23,22,"“Ndipo pa msana pa izo ndi pamwamba pa zombo, mumanyamulidwa"
  23,23,"“Ndipo ndithu tidamtuma Nuh kwa anthu ake, ndipo adati: “E inu anthu anga! Mpembedzeni Allah! Mulibe mulungu wina woti nkumpembedza kupatula Iye. Kodi simuopa (chilango Chake)"
  23,24,"“Akuluakulu mwa anthu ake amene sadakhulupirire, adati: “Uyu sali kanthu, koma ndi munthu ngati inu; akufuna kuti adzipezere ubwino pa inu; ndipo Allah akadafuna (kukuphunzitsani) akadatuma angelo. Zoterezi sitidamvepo kumakolo athu akale.”"
  23,25,"““Uyu sali kanthu, koma ndi munthu wamisala; choncho muyembekezereni mpaka nthawi (yofera.”)"
  23,26,"“(Nuh) adati: “Mbuye wanga ndipulumutseni pazomwe anditsutsa!”"
  23,27,"“Choncho tidamuvumbulutsira (mawu akuti): “Panga chombo moyang’aniridwa ndi kudziwitsidwa ndi Ife.” Ndipo lamulo Lathu likadza ndi kufwamphuka madzi mu uvuni, lowetsa mkati mwake (mwa chombocho) chilichonse ziwiriziwiri, chachimuna ndi chachikazi ndi banja lako, kupatula yemwe liwu latsogola pa iye kuti aonongeke mwa iwo. Ndipo usandilankhule za omwe adzichitira (okha) zoipa ndithu iwo amizidwa (m’madzi)"
  23,28,"“Ndipo ukakhazikika m’chombocho, iwe ndi amene uli nawo, nena: “Tikuthokoza Allah, amene watipulumutsa ku anthu osalungama.”"
  23,29,"“Ndipo (potsika), nena: “E Mbuye wanga! Nditsitseni; kutsitsa kwa madalitso, pakuti Inu ndinu wotsitsa bwino kwambiri kuposa otsitsa.”"
  23,30,“Ndithu m’zimenezi muli zisonyezo. Ndithu Ife tili (ndi udindo) wowayesa ndi mayeso osiyanasiyana
  23,31,“Kenako tidabweretsa m’badwo wina pambuyo pawo (omwe ndi Âdi)
  23,32,"“Ndipo tidatuma kwa iwo mtumiki (Hûd) wochokera mwa iwo, (yemwe ankati): “Pembedzani Allah! Mulibe mulungu wina kupatula Iye. Kodi simuopa"
  23,33,"“Ndipo akuluakulu a mwa anthu ake amene adali osakhulupirira, ndikutsutsa za kukumana ndi tsiku la chimaliziro, omwe tidawapatsa kulemera pa moyo wa padziko lapansi, adati: “Uyu saali kanthu, koma ndi munthu monga inu; amadya zimene inu mumadya, ndi kumwa zomwe inu mumamwa"
  23,34,"“Koma ngati mumvera munthu wonga inu, ndiye kuti mukhala otaika (oluza)"
  23,35,"“Kodi akukulonjezani kuti mukadzafa ndikusanduka dothi ndi mafupa, mudzaukitsidwanso (m’manda)"
  23,36,"“Sizingachitike, sizingachitike, zimene mukulonjezedwazi"
  23,37,“Palibe (moyo wina) koma moyo wathu wapadziko lapansiwu basi! Tikufa ndiponso kukhala ndi moyo! Ndipo sitidzaukitsidwa m’manda
  23,38,"“Uyu saali kanthu (amene akudzitcha kuti ndi Mtumiki) koma ndi munthu basi, akupekera Allah bodza, ndipo ife sitimkhulupirira.”"
  23,39,"“(Mtumikiyo) adati: “E Mbuye wanga! Ndipulumutseni pachifukwa chakuti anditsutsa.”"
  23,40,"“(Allah) adati: “Posachedwapa akhala odzinena.”"
  23,41,"“Choncho, mkuwe wa (chilango) choonadi udawaononga, ndipo tidawachita ngati zinyalala (zongotengedwa ndi madzi). Choncho, kuonongeka kudatsimikizika pa anthu osalungama"
  23,42,“Ndipo titatero tidalenga mibadwo ina pambuyo pawo
  23,43,“Palibe mtundu ungaifulumizitse kapena kuichedwetsa nthawi yake yofera
  23,44,"“Kenaka tidatuma atumiki Athu motsatizana; (wina pambuyo pa mnzake). Ndipo mbadwo uliwonse pamene adaufikira mtumiki wake, udamtsutsa; ndipo tidawaononga motsatana; ndipo tidawachita kukhala nkhani (za anthu.) Ndipo kuonongeka kudatsimikizika pa anthu osakhulupirira"
  23,45,"“Zitatero tidatuma Mûsa ndi m’bale wake Harun ndi zozizwitsa Zathu, ndi umboni woonekera poyera"
  23,46,“Kwa Farawo ndi nduna zake. Koma onse adadzitukumula; ndipo adali anthu odzikweza
  23,47,"“Ndipo adati: “Ha! Tikhulupirire anthu awiri onga ife, omwe mtundu wawo ndi akapolo athu!”"
  23,48,"“Choncho adawatsutsa onse awiri, ndipo adali m’gulu la oonongedwa"
  23,49,“Ndipo ndithu Mûsa tidampatsa buku kuti iwo aongoke
  23,50,"“Ndipo tidamchita mwana wa Mariya ndi mayi wake kukhala chisonyezo (choonetsa kukhoza kwathu). Ndipo tidawapatsa malo othawirapo, pachikweza, chokhazikika pomwenso padali akasupe"
  23,51,"“E inu Atumiki! Idyani zakudya zabwino, ndipo chitani zabwino. Ndithu Ine ndi Wodziwa zonse zimene muchita"
  23,52,"“(Tidauza mibadwo yawo): “Ndithu mpingo wanuwu ndi mpingo umodzi, ndipo Ine Ndine Mbuye wanu; choncho ndiopeni.”"
  23,53,“Koma adadula chinthu chawochi (chipembedzo chawo) pakati pawo mipatukomipatuko; gulu lililonse limasangalalira chimene lili nacho
  23,54,"“Choncho, asiye mu umbuli wawo kufikira nthawi (yakufa kwawo)"
  23,55,“Kodi akuganiza kuti tikamawapatsa chuma ndi ana
  23,56,"“Tikuwafulumizitsira zabwino? Sichoncho, koma iwo sakuzindikira"
  23,57,"“Ndithu amene amakhala amantha chifukwa choopa Mbuye wawo, (ndi m’mene mathero awo adzakhalire)"
  23,58,“Ndi omwe amakhulupirira Ayah za Mbuye wawo
  23,59,“Ndi omwenso saphatikiza Mbuye wawo ndi mafano
  23,60,"“Ndi omwenso amapereka (Zakaat ndi sadaka kuchokera m’chuma) chimene apatsidwa, uku mitima yawo ili yoopa kuti adzabwerera kwa Mbuye wawo"
  23,61,"“Amenewa ndiamene akuchita changu pa zinthu zabwino, ndipo iwo akutsogolera (ena) pa zimenezo"
  23,62,"“Ndipo sitikakamiza munthu, koma chimene angathe (kuchichita). Ndipo tili naye kaundula (wosunga chilichonse) yemwe adzayankhula choonadi ndipo iwo sadzaponderezedwa"
  23,63,"“Koma mitima yawo ili m’kusalabadira mu ichi; ndipo iwo ali ndi ntchito zimene akuchita, osati izi"
  23,64,"“Kufikira tikadzawaika m’chilango amene ali opeza bwino awo, pompo adzakuwa (ndi kupempha chipulumutso)"
  23,65,"“(Kudzanenedwa kwa iwo): “Musalire lero (ndi kupempha chipulumutso)! Ndithu inu simupulumutsidwa ndi Ife.”"
  23,66,““Ndipo Ayah Zanga zinkawerengedwa kwa inu koma munkadzibwezera kumbuyo ndi zidendene zanu
  23,67,“Uku mukudzikweza; nkumakambirana usiku za chabechabe zoinyoza (Qur’an).”
  23,68,"“Kodi sadaganizire liwu (ili limene wadza nalo Mtumiki{s.a.w}), kapena zawadzera zomwe sizidawadzerepo makolo awo akale"
  23,69,“Kodi kapena sadam’dziwe Mtumiki wawoyu (makhalidwe ake) kotero kuti iwo akum’kana
  23,70,"“Kapena akunena kuti: “Ngwamisala?” Koma wawadzera ndi choonadi, ndipo ambiri a iwo amachida choonadi"
  23,71,"“Ndipo choonadi chikadatsatira zofuna zawo, ndiye kuti thambo ndi nthaka ndi za m’menemo zikadaonongeka! Koma tawabweretsera chikumbutso chawo, koma iwo akuchipewa chikumbutso chawocho"
  23,72,“Kodi kapena ukuwapempha malipiro (nchifukwa chake akuchikana chipembedzochi)? Koma malipiro a Mbuye wako ndiwo abwino; ndipo Iye ndi Wopereka Wabwino kuposa opereka
  23,73,“Ndipo ndithu iwe ukuwaitanira ku njira yolunjika; (supempha malipiro kwa iwo pa kuitanako)
  23,74,"“Ndipo ndithu amene sakhulupirira tsiku la chimaliziro, ali kutali ndi njira ya choonadi"
  23,75,"“Ndipo tikadawachitira chifundo ndi kuwachotsera masautso omwe ali nawo, ndithu akadapitiriza kuyumbayumba m’kuchita kwawo zoipa"
  23,76,"“Ndipo ndithu tidawalanga ndi chilango (chaukali), koma sadacheukire kwa Mbuye wawo ndikudzichepetsa"
  23,77,“Kufikira pamene tidawatsekulira khomo la chilango chaukali; pamenepo ndipo adataya mtima
  23,78,"“Ndipo Iye ndi Yemwe adakupangirani makutu, maso ndi mitima; nzochepa zimene mukuthokoza"
  23,79,“Iyenso ndi Yemwe wakufalitsani pa dziko; kenako mudzasonkhanitsidwa kwa Iye
  23,80,"“Ndipo Iye ndi Yemwe amapatsa moyo ndi imfa, ndipo kusinthana kwa usiku ndi usana Nkwake. Kodi simuzindikira"
  23,81,“Koma akunena monga (anthu) oyamba adanenera
  23,82,"“Akunena: “Kodi tikadzafa ndikukhala dothi ndi mafupa, tidzaukitsidwanso?”"
  23,83,"““Ndithudi ife ndi makolo athu kale tidalonjezedwa zimenezi, izi sikanthu koma nkhambakamwa za anthu akale.”"
  23,84,"“Nena: “Kodi nthaka njayani ndi zomwe zili m’menemo, ngati inu mukudziwa (kanthu)!”"
  23,85,"“Adzanena kuti: “Nza Allah!” Nena: “Nanga bwanji simukumkumbukira (kuti Iye Ngokhoza chilichonse)"
  23,86,"“Nena: “Kodi ndani Mbuye wa thambo zisanu ndi ziwiri, ndi Mbuye wa Arsh (Mpando wachifumu) yaikulu?”"
  23,87,"“Anena (kuti): “Nza Allah.” Nena: “Nanga bwanji simukumuopa?”"
  23,88,"“Nena: “Kodi ndani yemwe m’manja mwake muli mphamvu yolamulira chinthu chilichonse? Ndipo Iye amateteza zonse. Ndipo palibe chimene chingatetezedwe kuchilango Chake. Ngati inu mukudziwa.”"
  23,89,"“Anena (kuti): “Ndi Allah.” Nena: “Nanga mukulodzedwa bwanji (ndi satana)?”"
  23,90,“Koma tawabweretsera choonadi; ndithu iwo ngabodza (potsutsana ndi choonadicho)
  23,91,"“Allah sadadzipangire mwana, ndipo padalibe pamodzi ndi Iye mulungu (wina), ngati zikadakhala choncho ndiye kuti mulungu aliyense akadatenga zimene adalenga, ndipo milungu ina ikadaipambana milungu inzawo (polimbanirana ufumu), Allah wapatukana nazo kwambiri zimene akusimbazo"
  23,92,“Wodziwa zamseri ndi zapoyera; watukuka ku zimene akumphatikiza nazozo
  23,93,"“Nena: “E Mbuye wanga! Ngati mungandionetse zomwe akulonjezedwa (ndikadali ndi moyo)"
  23,94,“E Mbuye wanga! Musandiyike m’gulu la anthu osalungama.”
  23,95,“Ndipo ndithu Ife ndi Wokhoza kukuonetsa (chilango) chimene tikuwalonjeza
  23,96,“Chotsa zoipa (zimene akukuchitira) powabwezera zabwino; Ife tikudziwa zimene akunena
  23,97,"“Ndipo nena: “E Mbuye wanga! Ndikudzitchinjiriza ndi Inu kumanong’onong’o a satana.”"
  23,98,““Ndiponso ndikudzitchinjiriza ndi inu Mbuye wanga kuti asandidzere.”
  23,99,"“Kufikira m’modzi wawo ikam’dzera imfa, amanena: “Mbuye wanga! Ndibwezereni (ku moyo wa pa dziko),”"
  23,100,"““Kuti ndikachite zabwino pa zimene ndidasiya.” (Angelo amayankha kuti): “Iyayi! Ndithu awa ndi mawu basi amene iye akuyankhula (imfa ikamfika).” Ndipo patsogolo pawo pali chiyembekezo; (moyo wamasautso kwa oipa; ndipo wamtendere kwa abwino) kufikira tsiku limene adzaukitsidwa"
  23,101,"“Choncho, lipenga likadzaimbidwa, sipadzakhala chibale pakati pawo tsiku limenelo, ndipo sadzafunsana"
  23,102,"“Tsono omwe mlingo (wa zochita zawo zabwino) udzalemere, iwowo ndiwo opambana"
  23,103,"“Ndipo omwe miyeso yawo (ya zochita zabwino) idzatsike, iwowo ndi omwe adadziluzitsa okha; adzakhala ku Jahannam nthawi yaitali"
  23,104,"“Moto ukawawula nkhope zawo, ndipo adzakhala m’menemo uku mano ali pamtunda"
  23,105,"“(Adzauzidwa): “Kodi Ayah Zanga sizidali kuwerengedwa kwa inu ndipo inu nkumazitsutsa?”"
  23,106,"“Adzati: “Mbuye wathu! Zoipa zathu zidatigonjetsa, choncho tidali anthu osokera.”"
  23,107,"“Mbuye wathu! Titulutseni umu (m’moto ndikutibwezera ku dziko lapansi kuti tikachite ntchito yabwino); ngati titabwerezanso kuchita zoipa, ndiye kuti tidzakhaladi oipa (odziononga tokha).”"
  23,108,"“(Allah) adzati: “Khalani chete m’menemo, monyozeka! Ndipo musandilankhule!”"
  23,109,"“Ndithu mwa akapolo anga lidalipo gulu lomwe linkanena: “Mbuye wathu! Takhulupirira; choncho tikhululukireni ndi kutichitira chifundo; ndipo inu Ngabwino kwambiri kuposa (ena onse) ochita chifundo.”"
  23,110,““Koma inu mudawachita chipongwe kufikira adakuiwalitsani kundikumbuka uku muli kuwaseka.”
  23,111,““Ndithu Ine lero ndawalipira (Munda wamtendere) chifukwa cha kupirira kwawo; kuti ndithu iwo ndiwo opambana.”
  23,112,"“Adzanena: “Kodi mudakhala nthawi yotani padziko pa chiwerengero cha zaka?”"
  23,113,"“Adzayankha: “Tidakhala tsiku limodzi kapena gawo la tsiku; afunse owerengera.” (Adzatero poyerekeza ndi kutalika kwa moyo wamasautso ku Moto)"
  23,114,"“Adzanena: “Inu simudakhale (kudzikoko) koma pang’ono basi, mukadakhala mukudziwa (chilango chomwe chakufikanichi, sibwenzi mukuchita zoipa).”"
  23,115,"“Kodi mumaganiza kuti tidakulengani chabe, ndikuti simudzabwerera kwa Ife"
  23,116,"“Watukuka Allah, Mfumu ya choonadi; palibe wompembedza mwachoonadi koma Iye, Bwana wa Arsh (Mpando wachifumu) yolemekezeka (kwambiri)"
  23,117,"“Ndipo amene apembedza mulungu wina pomphatikiza ndi Allah, chikhalirecho iye alibe umboni pa zimenezo; basi chiwerengero chake chili kwa Mbuye wake. Ndithu osakhulupirira sangapambane"
  23,118,"“Choncho nena: “Mbuye wanga! Ndikhululukireni ndikundichitira Chifundo! Inu Ngabwino kuposa achifundo.”"